text: Ærest of þaem ge mannan treowe on bogeles pearruc.
Of boceles pearruce on hrytmes mere of hrytmes mere on þone blacan mor of þam blacan more on imba lea.
Of imba lea on wernan wylle.
Of gyrd forda on ecgstanes stan of ecgstanes stane on gunredes ford of gunredes forda on seofan aec of seofan acon on hylnes lea of hylnes lea on braccan heal of brachan heale.
On ruwan beorg of ruwan beorge on teappan treow of tappan treow on uuest leas hagan of uuest leas hagan on ceauuan hrycges hagan of ceauuan hrycges hagan eft on þæt ge mæne treow.
